➜92+31+21！绿凯四核放下成见同仇敌忾，逆转入总决概率升至28%
http://www.sohu.com/a/419606340_343291	12110
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200920/2892633b388b40759f630f7c963d287f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
